description:
The Banjo Juice Jazz Band plays 1920s Jazz, blues and swing! The group features Tyler Westcott (of Folkfaces) on guitar, trumpet, banjo and vocals! Kyle Ohlson (Of Pine Fever) on Clarinet and sax. Kyle Yagielski (of The Buffalo Brass Machine) on Sousaphone, trumpet, and trombone and whoever else joins us!

8-11pm $5
name: Banjo Juice Jazz Band At Funk 'n Waffles Music Hall
